                    71-72 (source of the text reproduced here). <emph>Document summaries</emph>:
                    RIM, 353. <emph>Fac simile</emph>: Galasso 1967, tavv. 7-8.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="additional">
                <p/>
            </div>
